item.title: CONAN THE BARBARIAN - Theatrical Trailer
item.description:
CONAN THE BARBARIAN - Theatrical Trailer
"I live. I love. I slay...I am content." - Conan The Barbarian The most legendary Barbarian of all time is back this Summer. Having thrived and evolved for eight consecutive decades in the public imagination- in prose and graphics, on the big screen and small, in games and properties of all kinds- Conan's exploits in the Hyborian Age now come alive like never before in a colossal 3D action-adventure film. more... A quest that begins as a personal vendetta for the fierce Cimmerian warrior soon turns into an epic battle against hulking rivals, horrific monsters, and impossible odds, as Conan realizes he is the only hope of saving the great nations of Hyboria from an encroaching reign of supernatural evil. Deftly adapted from the original works of Robert E. Howard and faithful to the mythology and psychology of his iconic character, CONAN THE BARBARIAN stars Jason Momoa, Rachel Nichols, Stephen Lang, Rose McGowan, Saïd Taghmaoui and Ron Perlman. The film is directed by Marcus Nispel, and written by Thomas Dean Donnelly & Joshua Oppenheimer and Sean Hood.

item.title: Summoner Showcase - Issue #27
item.description:
Summoner Showcase - Issue #27
Play League of Legends for Free: Play League of Legends FREE at http://signup.leagueoflegends.com/?ref=SSIssue27 Let's get up close and personal with the entries that make this video great! Galactic Renekton Chibi [http://crissaegrimdust.deviantart.com/art/LoL-Chibi-Galactic-Renekton-206435293] CrissargrimDust transforms Renekton into a cuddly version of his existing self. Don't be fooled; the cute demeanor is just a disguise for a cold, reptilian heart underneath ... or perhaps no heart at all. Sigh. Teemo Toy [http://www.leagueoflegends.com/board/showthread.php?t=617661] NoisyBonez designed Teemo like we've never seen him before: Cubed. And with a clever use of some homemade props, we now have a little Teemo doll with tiny mushrooms. Miss Fortune Art [http://achibner.deviantart.com/art/Miss-Fortune-199343895] QuickAndEasy gives us the shock and ahhhh with this dramatic and beautiful Miss Fortune digital painting. Welcome to Summoner's Rift (HARSH LANGUAGE WARNING!) [http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SxPFijOpdlo] Cody and Collective tear it up on the mic with their song parody. They keep it real and from the lane, but there is some offensive language -- beware, younger summoners! Cho'Gath vs Ryze [http://nyra119.deviantart.com/art/Cho-gath-vs-Ryze-202427998] Nyra blows us away with this new painting of a fearsome face-off. Will the Goliath resist the rune prison? We wish we knew. That's all for this week! If you find anything incredible you need to include, send a link with your summoner name to Summoner_Showcase@RiotGames.com! We'll see you next week! By the way, the Annie Bot shirt is in the NA Merch Store! http://merch.leagueoflegends.com/catalog/view/76 The EU store launch is on its way, thanks for being patient!
